---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---

{% if carousel.length > 0 %}
<div class="carousel">
  <div class="carousel-track" id="carousel-track">
    {% for item in carousel %}
      <img src="{{ item }}" alt="Dance photo {{ loop.index }}">
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <button class="carousel-btn carousel-prev" aria-label="Previous photo">&#8249;</button>
  <button class="carousel-btn carousel-next" aria-label="Next photo">&#8250;</button>
  <div class="carousel-dots" id="carousel-dots"></div>
</div>
{% endif %}

<section class="hero container">
  <h1>Dance With Us<br><span class="gradient">Every Thursday</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">West Coast Swing in Albuquerque — beginner lessons, social dancing, and a community that welcomes everyone. No partner or experience needed.</p>
  <div class="hero-cta">
    <a href="/events/" class="btn">See Upcoming Events</a>
    <a href="/about/" class="btn secondary">Learn More</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="weekly-info">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="info-bar">
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-icon">📅</span>
        <div>
          <strong>Every Thursday</strong>
          <span>7:00 PM – 10:00 PM</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-divider"></div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-icon">📍</span>
        <div>
          <strong>Lloyd Shaw Dance Center</strong>
          <span>3201 Juan Tabo Blvd NE, ABQ</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-divider"></div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="info-icon">🎓</span>
        <div>
          <strong>Beginner Lesson Included</strong>
          <span>7:00–7:45 PM every week</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="container">
  <h2 class="section-heading">Everyone's Welcome Here</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🌱</div>
      <h3>No Experience Needed</h3>
      <p>We start fresh every week with a beginner lesson. You can walk in having never danced a step and leave knowing how to West Coast Swing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🤝</div>
      <h3>No Partner Needed</h3>
      <p>We rotate partners throughout the night. Come alone, come with friends — everyone dances with everyone.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">🌍</div>
      <h3>Truly Inclusive</h3>
      <p>We're welcoming to all regardless of age, background, gender, or skill level. Lead, follow, or both — you decide.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% set now = "now" | toMillis %}
{% set upcomingEvents = [] %}
{% for event in events | sort(attribute="date") %}
  {% if event.date | toMillis >= now %}
    {% set upcomingEvents = (upcomingEvents.push(event), upcomingEvents) %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if upcomingEvents.length > 0 %}
<section class="next-event-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Next Up</h2>
    {% set next = upcomingEvents[0] %}
    <div class="card next-event-card">
      <div class="next-event-info">
        <p class="event-date">{{ next.date | date("EEEE, MMMM d, yyyy") }}</p>
        <h3>{{ next.title }}</h3>
        <p class="event-location">{{ next.location }}{% if next.address %} · {{ next.address }}{% endif %}</p>
        {% for paragraph in next.description %}
          <p>{{ paragraph }}</p>
        {% endfor %}
        <a href="/events/" class="btn" style="margin-top: 1rem;">All Upcoming Events</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section class="what-is-wcs">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="wcs-grid">
      <div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">What Is West Coast Swing?</h2>
        <p>West Coast Swing is a partner dance with a distinctive elastic, slotted style. Unlike many partner dances, it's completely music-agnostic — it works with blues, pop, country, hip-hop, R&B, and pretty much anything with a beat.</p>
        <p>It's a <strong>social dance</strong>, which means the steps are improvised in conversation with your partner rather than choreographed. That's what makes it endlessly fun to learn: every dance is different.</p>
        <a href="/about/" class="btn secondary" style="margin-top: 1rem;">More About Us</a>
      </div>
      <div class="wcs-facts card">
        <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
        <ul class="facts-list">
          <li>Partner dance — no prior dance experience needed</li>
          <li>Works with virtually any music genre</li>
          <li>Roles are not gender-assigned — lead or follow your choice</li>
          <li>Albuquerque has a friendly, active WCS community</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
